Deploy main.py to a cloud function with

gcloud functions deploy cwltool_salad --runtime python37 --trigger-http

cwltool-runner {
  class = "cwl.CwltoolHttp"
  config.url = <your cloud function url>
}

That's it !

----------------

The local_server.py can be used to debug the function locally.
Pre-requisite: Python 3.7, Flask
